    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The teachers and faculty members are good.",
          "name": "Nirjhara",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like our library as we have many useful study materials.",
          "name": "Nirjhara",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the labs seemed to be very nice and clean",
          "name": "Keren Subba",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Library was pretty good, canteen food was cheap though it was not tasty,our college gardens looks decent then the classes",
          "name": "Nazrina Khatoon",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Study material very clearly provided and easy to learn",
          "name": "Prasansa Moktan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Advanced technology used in labs and clean",
          "name": "Prasansa Moktan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the teachers being so polite and frankly",
          "name": "Prasansa Moktan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "This college is absolutely ragging free college",
          "name": "Ashadur jaman Haque",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus life with friends is full of enjoyment",
          "name": "MD rakhif alam",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the teachers how they teach and treat us very well",
          "name": "MD rakhif alam",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The mathematics department used to look like hunted house with no maintenance at all the doors were creaky and shagging the window were broken.",
          "name": "Nazrina Khatoon",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The canteen was so small,the classroom were very dusty,the playground was good though it was not very big. Coming to teacher they were well qualified but we were not able to catch them properly they used to rush ,and hurry to complete the syllabus",
          "name": "Nazrina Khatoon",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers Not following the time tableproperly",
          "name": "Prasansa Moktan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "No proper instruction instructed during labs",
          "name": "Prasansa Moktan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College don't have a boys hostel on the other hand college has 4 girls hostel",
          "name": "Ashadur jaman Haque",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our department was too small, we have only 2 professor and 1 sact teacher. The all are lady teacher",
          "name": "Ashadur jaman Haque",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I don't like when teacher doesn't comes to class section to teach there is no timing",
          "name": "MD rakhif alam",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lab has equipment but is not usable and it is broken .",
          "name": "Babina Rai",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some  teacher does not teach properly and just sit in office .",
          "name": "Babina Rai",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "NBU, Darjeeling"
    }
  },
